  "code": "stateDiagram\n  [*]-->Connecting\n  Connecting-->[*]\n  Connecting-->Connected\n  Connected-->Idle\n  Idle-->Sending\n  Sending-->Idle\n  Idle-->Timeout\n  Timeout-->[*]\n  Sending-->Timeout\n  Idle-->Closed\n  Closed-->[*]",
